						<div class="postbody">Hey,
<br />
<br />Anyone have the schematic handy to add 8k of sram to a TLROM pcb? I got a handful of extra SRAM chips and I wanna use them to make better use of my remaining TLROM boards. I know the sram can go pretty much pin for pin on the back of the PRG and still fit in the cart shell but what I'm not sure of is what the address lines are that have to be re-wired and exactly where they go on the mapper chip. 
<br />
<br />Thanks in advance,
<br />
<br />Shawn</div>

