						<div class="postbody">yeah just make sure you don't get confused on the pin numbering.  The first pin is to the left of the '1' on the PCB and goes counter clockwise from there with the last pin 44 being below the '1'. 
<br />
<br />It's not like you might think with the little dot being pin 1, that dot (the smaller one) is actually between pins 33 and 34.</div>

